summary: A compilation of of weapons from the game Alice: Madness Returns, including vorpal blades and hobby horses, and a few extras.
descriptionHtml:
A weapon pack consisting of weapons from Alice: Madness Returns.

Weapons included in this pack are the vorpal sword (and several variants), all of the different hobby horses (and a few new ones), adds a new dagger, a mace and some scythes.

These weapons can be forged in the Iron, Dwarven, Daedric, and Misc sections of any forge.

The vorpal blades, mace, and dagger are 1-hand weapons. The scythes, and hobby horses are 2-handed.

This mod should be compatible with everything. No DLC are required for this to run.

I found this file here([color=#1155cc]http://modtype.doorblog.jp/archives/11587064.html[/color]). It wasn't on the nexus or the workshop so I decided to put it here.
